00:28:00.782 --> 00:28:03.999
French soldiers,
and atrocities against peasants

00:28:03.999 --> 00:28:06.598
in Calabria in the south of
Italy.

00:28:06.598 --> 00:28:09.265
So, warfare really changes,
but it becomes a dynamic of

00:28:09.265 --> 00:28:09.710
change.
 

00:28:09.710 --> 00:28:13.108
If you think about the Russian
Revolution of 1917,

00:28:13.108 --> 00:28:16.519
the Russian Revolution was not
inconceivable without World War

00:28:16.519 --> 00:28:18.237
I,
but it was sort of

00:28:18.237 --> 00:28:22.630
inconceivable without the
Russian Revolution of 1905,

00:28:22.630 --> 00:28:27.320
and the defeat by the Japanese
in an extraordinary shocking

00:28:27.320 --> 00:28:30.585
event,
at least for Europeans in 1904

00:28:30.585 --> 00:28:31.430
and 1905.
 

00:28:31.430 --> 00:28:35.393
And World War I provides
opportunities for dissidents in

00:28:35.393 --> 00:28:38.058
Russia to put forward their
claims.

00:28:38.058 --> 00:28:41.840
So, when the whole thing
collapses on the czar's head in

00:28:41.840 --> 00:28:44.561
February 1917,
and the Bolsheviks come to

00:28:44.561 --> 00:28:47.381
power,
the war itself was a dynamic of

00:28:47.381 --> 00:28:48.589
change as well.
 

00:28:48.589 --> 00:28:50.289
And what a war.
 

00:28:50.289 --> 00:28:51.298
What wars.
 

00:28:51.298 --> 00:28:53.460
There have been nothing ever
like it.

00:28:53.460 --> 00:28:57.867
A few journalists who had been
