going to destroy four

00:29:07.894 --> 00:29:11.829
empires--the Ottoman empire,
the Austro-Hungarian empire,

00:29:11.829 --> 00:29:15.807
the German empire,
and the Russian empire,

00:29:15.807 --> 00:29:18.305
and, arguably,
we can talk about this and we

00:29:18.305 --> 00:29:20.230
can debate this,
the British empire.

00:29:20.230 --> 00:29:24.358
Because lots of people who had
fought in India,

00:29:24.358 --> 00:29:26.140
Indians who had fought in the
war,

00:29:26.140 --> 00:29:28.606
